relativeLogExpression.Rd

Relative log expression

relativeLogExpression(object, ...)

# S4 method for matrix
relativeLogExpression(object)

# S4 method for SummarizedExperiment
relativeLogExpression(object)

Arguments

object

Object.
...

Additional arguments.

Value

matrix.

Note

Updated 2020-01-20.

References

Anders and Huber (2010).

See also

edgeR::calcNormFactors().
